            <thetext>IE7

- Doubleclick on a table row or a column
- Fast third click outside the table or column
-&gt; the mouseevent (dblclick) contains a wrong pageX value (the value of the third click)

You can test it here (it is not easy to reproduce, maybe you have to try it several times):
http://demo.qooxdoo.org/current/demobrowser/#example~Table_1.html
- double click on the third column 
- fast third click on the second column
-&gt; the edit mode of the third column should be opened -&gt; instead the edit mode of the second column opens
-&gt; sometime there is a browser error (I don&#39;t know, if this is the same issue):
...&#39;this._inputElement&#39; is null or not an object...</thetext>
